data.description: This lovely home boasts several updates, including a new roof, new windows, a modern kitchen, and newer mechanicals. Walk through the front door and into the spacious sunroom, then into the living room offering plenty of natural light. The open-plan living space flows into the kitchen, featuring white cabinets and newer appliances. The master bedroom has an attached full, updated bathroom. The den is large and versatile, with a big closet, washer and dryer hookups, and the potential to be used as a third bedroom. Enjoy a fully fenced yard and a new storage shed. Make sure not to overlook the raised flower beds and the outdoor oasis, perfect for cozy bonfire gatherings!
